description: Changes include changing around some chord positions during the riffs, as the version on the site is not accurate to how Chuck played this song. The solos are also changed... The first tapping section that's on here currently is an unnecessarily difficult way to voice these tapping sections. For reference to how Chuck plays this song I used this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gsbRSX-3wBM
title: Born Dead (Corrected)
